result.name: Ocean Empire Food Shop

reviews.text: The food I had was pretty good and the service was fast.
With aircon here and the restaurant is spacious. Food is nice and the price is reasonable. The chee cheong fun and fried noodles are delicious.
Staff bit rude as they not wanna walk to take orders, sometimes. You may shout for orders....
Cheerful stuff who try to help even that they don't speak English. The menu has English though.
Average food at reasonable price.
